"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131762","Department for Exiting the European Union ","false","2019-06-18","<p>Details on the UK Statistics Authority’s interventions are published in the <a href="https://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/correspondence-list/" target="_blank">correspondence</a>, <a href="https://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/publications-list/" target="_blank">publications</a>, and <a href="https://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/reports-and-correspondence/issues-log/" target="_blank">issues log</a> sections of their website since 2010.</p><p>The Authority’s Office for Statistics Regulation (OSR) also carry out regular assessments and systemic reviews, details of which can also be found on the <a href="https://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/osr/" target="_blank">Authority’s website</a>.</p><p>In September 2018, the Authority published the first annual summary of its <a href="https://www.statisticsauthority.gov.uk/publication/annual-casework-review-20172018/" target="_blank">interventions for the financial year 2017/18</a>. The report for 2018/19 will be published in the autumn.</p>","Spelthorne","Kwasi Kwarteng",,"2019-06-18T12:45:44.577Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131762/answer","Biography information for Kwasi  Kwarteng","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131762/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131762/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union ","Exiting the European Union ","2019-06-12","Department for Exiting the European Union: Statistics","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, on how many occasions his Department has received representations from the UK Statistics Authority on his Department's presentation and use of statistics in each year since 2010.","false","Biography information for Chris Ruane","Vale of Clwyd","Chris Ruane","263733"
