"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131204","Cabinet Office","false","2019-06-17","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p>","Torbay","Kevin Foster",,"2019-06-17T11:24:49.71Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131204/answer","Biography information for Kevin Foster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131204/answer","PQ 263081.pdf","PQ 263081.pdf","UKSA response","UKSA response","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131204/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2019-06-11","Employment: Older People","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how many people over 70 are in (a) full- and (b) part-time employment.","false","Biography information for Mr Gregory Campbell","East Londonderry","Mr Gregory Campbell","263081"
