"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131284","Cabinet Office","false","2019-06-24","<p>The civil service looks to recognise the success and contribution of its staff throughout the year. There are currently no plans to organise events to support Public Service Day.</p>","Hertsmere","Oliver Dowden",,"2019-06-24T14:24:41.117Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131284/answer","Biography information for Oliver Dowden","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131284/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1131284/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2019-06-11","Public Service Day","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what plans the Government has to support Public Service Day on the 23 June 2019.","false","Biography information for Peter Kyle","Hove","Peter Kyle","263195"
